Title:
In Date/Time field button Hoy is not available.

User stories:
As a user, I want to be able to click the button HOY, so I can select the actual
date.

Description:
When the user open the calendar he or she see that
the actual date is selected for example today, but whe the user select
a day before on the same month the button HOY is not available of reason.

Steps to reproduce
    1. Open the Application.
    2. On the top select Urgency
    3. Select a patient.
    4. Go to Hoja SOAPE and click Anadir.
    5. In the Anadir button select Diagnostics.
    6. In Buscador diagnosticos codificados add TUMOR MALIGNO DE LA CABEZA, CARA Y CUELLO.
    7. In Gestor de diagnosticos click button Editar.
    8. Click on Fecha de aviso.
    9. On Date/Time field select a date before the actual date.

    Actual result: The button HOY is not available for the user.
    Expected result: The button HOY should be able for the user.
